People Think Jay Z Is Taking Shots at Drake on "Shining" By Zach Frydenlund Follow Zach on Twitter for jokes and hot takes here .
 Image via Publicist Whenever a new Jay Z verse comes out, the bars are broken down for hours on end. And for good reason, for 20 years he's being doing this. With his new verse on DJ Khaled's "Shining" single out , people are noticing that Hov might have sent some subtle shots at Drake on the song. Peep the bars in question:
